      <title>卡马拉·哈里斯承诺访问受风暴袭击的北卡罗来纳州并提供援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/kamala-harris-offers-aid-pledges-on-visit-to-storm-hit-north-carolina</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯在北卡罗来纳州会见了救援官员和志愿者，以表达对飓风海伦的受害者的支持，这场飓风给这个选举战场州造成了大规模的破坏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/kamala-harris-offers-aid-pledges-on-visit-to-storm-hit-north-carolina</guid>
