    <item>
      <title>一名幼儿和另外三人在试图横渡英吉利海峡时死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-05/attempts-to-cross-the-english-channel-on-small-boats-leave-4-migrants-including-a-child-dead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴黎（美联社）——法国当局称，周六，四名移民（其中包括一名 2 岁儿童）在试图穿越英吉利海峡前往英国时在两起独立事件中死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-05/attempts-to-cross-the-english-channel-on-small-boats-leave-4-migrants-including-a-child-dead</guid>
