    <item>
      <title>出口民调预测莫迪的对手将在邦选举中获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/exit-polls-predict-win-for-modi-s-opponents-in-state-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[出口民调显示，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的印度人民党在最近两次邦选举中落后，由于执政联盟在全国选举中的支持率较弱，这给反对党提供了助力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/exit-polls-predict-win-for-modi-s-opponents-in-state-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 16:02:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞内加尔承诺在评级下调后迅速采取行动弥补预算缺口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/senegal-pledges-swift-action-on-budget-gap-after-ratings-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔表示，将迅速采取行动降低预算赤字。审计显示该国财政和债务状况较弱，导致穆迪评级下调了该国的评级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/senegal-pledges-swift-action-on-budget-gap-after-ratings-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 15:26:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列袭击黎巴嫩，袭击贝鲁特郊区和北部</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-05/israel-strikes-lebanon-hitting-beirut-suburbs-and-the-north</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黎巴嫩马斯纳边境口岸（美联社）——星期六晚间，强烈的爆炸震动了贝鲁特南部郊区，以色列扩大了对黎巴嫩的轰炸，并首次袭击了黎巴嫩北部的一个巴勒斯坦难民营，因为以色列同时针对真主党和哈马斯战士。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-05/israel-strikes-lebanon-hitting-beirut-suburbs-and-the-north</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 11:44:38 GMT</pubDate>
